DRIVING RANGE RATES
Large-       $9.00
Small-       $4.50
20 Large-  $130
40 Large-  $180
Discount Cards Available In Pro Shop
Hours:  7:00 am until dusk.  Range closes by 3:30 on Sunday to accommodate mowing.
Contact the Pro Shop with questions.
MEMBERSHIP RATES
ASSOCIATE GOLF MEMBERSHIP
Associate Memberships are available for residents and non-residents.
Note:  An R.O. share is not required to purchase an Associate Membership.
Golf Memberships may be purchase at the Continental Country Club Administration office Monday through Thursday 9:00am – 3:30pm. Telephone:  352-748-9227
Payment plans are available
